data.value: Where: L: span length. d: beam depth "Cover removed". C: column width. b: Minimum width of concrete section. W: distributed load. fcu: Concrete compressive strength. fy: stirrups yield stress. P: concentrated load. a: concentrated load location. Qcr: shear force at Critical section or Qcracked. qu: Shear stress. q uncr: uncracked concrete shear strength. q cr: cracked concrete shear strength. qu max: maximum section shear strength. S: spacing between stirrups. As = area of one branch of the stirrup.
